name: Christy Harrison
title: Photographer, Digital Artist, Textile Designer
summary: International Award Winning, Fine Art Photographer focused on commercial, portrait, fashion, wedding, landscapes, and textile design. Exceptional skill set as well as innovative creativity in studio and on location, with eight years experience in conjunction with the honor of being published. My objective is to inspire others using my photography gift.

Collection has expanded to include jewelry, yoga/leisure wear, and home collection.
